<span class="global-warning">
This site is likely to contain content that you may want to avoid; please exercise caution and self-care as a priority.
[ {{link-to 'admin' 'admin'}} ]
</span>
    
<header>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <h1>
        {{#link-to "index"}}
          Flowerpot
        {{/link-to}} 
      </h1>
      <h2>An app for safe content sharing.</h2>

      {{link-to "Create New Pot" 'posts.new' class="button create-new"}} or <a href="#">see an example</a>?
      {{#if showIndex.showIndex}}
        {{link-to "list of posts (beta only)" "posts.index" class="button"}}
      {{/if}}
    </div>
  </div>
</header>
   
<div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="column">
        {{outlet}}
      </div>
    </div>
</div>

<footer>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row" id="info">
      <div class="column">
        <h4>Want to know more?</h4>
        <p>If you'd like to learn more about Flowerpot, there's more info in the {{link-to "FAQ" "mdContent" "questions"}},  {{link-to "Code of Conduct" "mdContent" "code-of-conduct" class=""}}, and {{link-to "Privacy" "mdContent" "privacy" class=""}} information. </p>
          
        <p>For more technical information, we have a {{link-to "Technical FAQ" "mdContent" "technical-questions"}} as well as a {{link-to "Getting Started Guide" "mdContent" "getting-started" class=""}}. Our Github repo is located <a href="https://github.com/ibroadfo/flowerpot">here</a>.</p>
           
           <h4>Got a question? Want to help?</h4>
           <p>Please do <a href="#">get in touch</a> if you have a question that's gone unanswered, or if you want to contribute but don't feel comfortable with Github. We'd love to hear from you!</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
